    "description": "In <strong>Rerun</strong> you must cunningly wield your adventurer's <strong>ever-evolving</strong> abilities or end up out of usages and doomed to an endless struggle. Using the environment to your advantage, <strong>position</strong> your chaotic adventurers to keep them safe and <strong>lure your foes</strong> into your <strong>devious traps</strong> that'll send them flying into <strong>lava!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161130/extras/0f28774287f9bf46d8c26ec88fe36c14.poster.avif?t=1685363190\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161130/extras/0f28774287f9bf46d8c26ec88fe36c14.webm?t=1685363190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161130/extras/0f28774287f9bf46d8c26ec88fe36c14.mp4?t=1685363190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Rerun plays like a combination of <i>Into the Breach</i> and <i>Slay the Spire</i>. Each playthrough a <strong>random dungeon map</strong> is generated <strong>which doubles as your skill tree,</strong> navigate the map and choose the perfect upgrades for your adventurers' abilities. And maybe.. be greedy and double down at certain levels to get <strong>extra rewards</strong> in preparation for the <strong>boss fights</strong>? Don't run out of ability usages though!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161130/extras/bfa191f33dfb3fab40b61718d834f8fe.poster.avif?t=1685363190\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161130/extras/bfa191f33dfb3fab40b61718d834f8fe.webm?t=1685363190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161130/extras/bfa191f33dfb3fab40b61718d834f8fe.mp4?t=1685363190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>21 Adventurer combinations</strong>, each providing new devious methods to bully foes.<br></li><li>Play through an <strong>ever-changing dungeon</strong> which doubles as your <strong>skill tree</strong>.<br></li><li>Choose from and equip <strong>over 80 wild upgrades</strong>.<br></li><li>Unlock <strong>7 quirky adventurers</strong> with <strong>over 40 unique abilities and items</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>Overcome 6 challenging boss encounters</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>Daily Mode</strong> where each day you can play as Chad &amp; Thad, two randomly generated adventurers.</li></ul>",
